➜紧急通知！2021.1.1英国脱欧后EORI无法在欧盟清关！
http://www.sohu.com/a/427436672_115514	31252
<p><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201026/792b0cede8204965b550171d7865df4b.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span><span>自从</span></span><span>2020<span>年</span><span>1</span><span>月</span><span>31</span><span>日英国</span></span><span><span>脱欧以来，英国</span></span><span><span>进入</span></span><span><span>了长达一年的</span></span><span><span>过渡期</span></span><span><span>。现有的政策可以</span></span><span><span>一直维持到</span>2020<span>年</span><span>12</span><span>月</span><span>31</span><span>日</span></span><span><span>，但</span></span><span><span>还有六十多天英国就要正式脱欧了，成为单一的市场。未来，</span></span><span><span>英国与欧盟之间将建立关税边界，这</span></span><span><span>会</span></span><span><span>影响</span></span><span><span>卖家们在欧洲的生意</span></span><span><span>。</span></span></p>
<p><span><span>虽然目前暂未得知</span>2021<span>年</span><span>1</span><span>月</span><span>1</span><span>日后，英国与欧盟的贸易协议的最终条款是什么，但近几日英国政府发表了一项声明，这个声明意味着卖家目前所持有的英国</span><span>EORI</span><span>号码只能在英国境内清关，而不能在其他欧盟国清关。从</span><span>2021</span><span>年</span><span>1</span><span>月</span><span>1</span><span>日开始，卖家向欧盟出口或进口商品时需要进行海关申报。这些规定目前适用于向世界其他地区出口货物，包括瑞士，挪威，冰岛和列支敦士登。</span></span></p>
<p><span>2021<span>年</span><span>1</span><span>月</span><span>1</span><span>日后，</span></span><span><span>如果</span></span><span><span>卖家只有英国</span>EORI<span>号码</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>那</span></span><span>HMRC<span>（英国税务与海关总署）</span></span><span><span>就</span></span><span><span>无法清算</span></span><span><span>卖家</span></span><span><span>的货物，则</span></span><span><span>卖家</span></span><span><span>可能需要支付</span></span><span><span>额外的</span></span><span><span>仓储费</span></span><span><span>，不仅</span></span><span><span>会延误</span></span><span><span>清关时间，还会</span></span><span><span>增加成本</span></span><span><span>。此外，如果卖家</span></span><span><span>要在</span></span><span><span>其他</span></span><span><span>欧盟</span></span><span><span>国</span></span><span><span>进行海关申报或获得海关</span></span><span><span>文件，也需要其他欧盟国的</span></span><span>EORI<span>号码</span></span><span><span>。</span></span></p>
<p><span><span>所以卖家当务之急</span></span><span><span>需要</span></span><span><span>申请</span></span><span><span>一个</span></span><span><span>欧盟国的</span></span><span>EORI<span>号码</span></span><span><span>和一个英国</span></span><span>EORI<span>号码</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>才能在英国和欧盟国之间转移货物</span></span><span><span>。卖家可以自己在欧洲各国税局官网</span></span><span><span>在线申请</span>EORI<span>号码，</span></span><span><span>大约耗时</span></span><span>10<span>分钟</span></span><span><span>；如果不懂外语，也可以在国内一些</span>VAT<span>在线申报平台申请；</span></span><span><span>但</span></span><span><span>各国</span></span><span>EORI</span><span><span>下发时间和生效时间不同</span></span><span><span>。</span></span></p>
<p><span><span>为了方便各位卖家自主申请欧洲国</span></span><span>EORI</span><span><span>，我们整理了欧洲各国税局官网的</span></span><span>EORI</span><span><span>申请页面，粘贴到游览器即可注册该国</span></span><span>EORI</span><span><span>号码。</span></span></p>
<p><span><span><strong>在线申请</strong></span></span><span><span><strong>英国</strong></span></span><span><strong>EORI</strong><span><strong>号码</strong></span></span></p>
