➜关于UPC
http://www.sohu.com/a/427451352_115514	37588
<p><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201026/136fc9453ce24a058dff8d051aeb9b47.jpeg" /></p>
<p>之前有发过一个关于豁免的但是大家还是要理性申请豁免。</p>
<p>UPC链接虽然容易被搞，但有弊也有利。</p>
<p>豁免只是预防VC，普通跟卖依然有机会获得编辑权，修改listing信息。</p>
<p>类似老鼠吃大象，大象吃老虎，老虎吃老鼠的规则。</p>
<p>有时候，如果你有UPC证书，拿回编辑权反倒更容易。</p>
<p><span>市场上UPC来源</span></p>
<p>1. GS1官网直接购买。亚马逊认可。购买成本略高。</p>
<p>2. barcodestalk.com处购买的，理论上他们是代理，所以在GS1上查询所有人并不是你。但它们网站可查购买记录，你公司信息是对得上的，多开case，部分客服会认可。</p>
<p>3. 其他不明来源，或者生成器直接生成的，听天由命吧。</p>
<p><span>查询UPC归属</span>：www.ancc.org.cn/Service/queryTools/External.aspx</p>
<p>如图示，显示该UPC归属企业是苹果。</p>
<p><img src="//p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201026/6689391f09174fcfa45b9059e4290222.png" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p>也可以直接去GS1官网查询：https://gepir.gs1.org/index.php/search-by-gtin</p>
<p><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201026/9bf967b1cbc743598cd8c07c0a70763f.png" /></p>
<p>如果是代理商处购买UPC，比如https://www.barcodestalk.com</p>
<p>它也会有一个证书查询地址： https://www.barcodestalk.com/gepir</p>
<p>上面有显示购买公司，联系方式，UPC号码段</p>
<p><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201026/a7c05d13fc444def9ab6e52b09ac350f.png" /></p>
<p><span>Listing为什么会被人修改？</span></p>
<p>这是一个老生常谈的话题，任何ASIN所有权都是属于亚马逊，卖家只拥有编辑权。</p>
<p>VC的编辑权最大，其次是占据buybox的卖家。</p>
<p>所以，只要谁占据buybox，谁就拥有编辑权。</p>
<p>有人跟卖你，自然他会有占据buybox的机会。</p>
<p>比较少见的是跨站点跟卖，这种就比较猥琐。</p>
<p>常见的连锁反应：图片等信息被改，变体突然自动拆分且合不上。</p>
<p><span>如果listing被修改，怎么应对呢？</span></p>
<p><span>图片或者关键信息被修改，记得先停售再申请更改。</span></p>
<p>普通跟卖：</p>
<p>先模板刷新listing在后台的信息</p>
<p>准备带品牌logo，upc（最好是印上去的）的包装图片</p>
<p>去页面修复路径或者report violation路径</p>
<p>Dear Amazon,</p>
<p>My listing was hijacked by someone, the images/ brand/ title...was changed into a completely different product. You can check the history of this ASIN XXX.</p>
<p>The hijacker's behavior will not only affect my sales, but also bring bad experiences to customers. </p>
<p>I need your help to fix it.</p>
<p>上传产品包装，官网证明</p>
<p>跨站点跟卖，图片被同步：</p>
<p>先模板刷新listing在后台的信息</p>
<p><span>找到目标站点</span></p>
<p>进入report violation路径</p>
<p>Dear Amazon,</p>
<p>I would like to report that someone is abusing our UPC code and selling item on XXX marketplace. As a result, the images/ brand/ title...my ASIN XX was changed into a completely different product. You can check the history of this ASIN XXX.</p>
<p>The hijacker's behavior will not only affect my sales, but also bring bad experiences to customers. </p>
<p>I need your help to fix it. </p>
<p>The attachment is the licensee of my UPC from GS1.(代理商的就发对应查询链接)</p>
<p>上传UPC证明, 耐心等待回复</p>
